sequenceDiagram
    participant Thread A
    participant Atomic Value
    participant Thread B

    Note over Atomic Value: value = 5

    Thread A->>Atomic Value: load() → 5
    Thread B->>Atomic Value: load() → 5

    Note over Thread A: compute: 5 + 1 = 6
    Note over Thread B: compute: 5 + 2 = 7

    Thread A->>Atomic Value: CAS(5, 6) → Success
    Note over Atomic Value: value = 6

    Thread B->>Atomic Value: CAS(5, 7) → Fails (actual = 6)
    Note over Thread B: retry with new value

    Thread B->>Atomic Value: load() → 6
    Note over Thread B: compute: 6 + 2 = 8
    Thread B->>Atomic Value: CAS(6, 8) → Success
    Note over Atomic Value: value = 8
